{"tid":1607047,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"BE WATER 的真締","createTime":"2019-09-30T17:13:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T17:38:13.000Z","uid":298707,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fb5eb9770f94a41af3ab73c0a4c418a36226f81f","tid":1607047,"uid":298707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:13:51.000Z","msg":"各位手足<br />\n<br />\n係呢度想講下, BE WATER 唔等於走佬逃跑<br />\n不如一齊重溫李小龍既金句<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Water can <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">flow</span> or it can <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">crash</span><br />\nBe water, my friend.&rdquo;<br />\n水可以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">流動</span>, 亦能<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">衝擊</span><br />\n像水一樣吧，朋友<br />\n<br />\n李小龍講be water 既意思, 唔係叫你留得青山在<br />\n你有幾時見過李小龍逃跑?<br />\nBe water 係叫大家隨機應變, 適當時應對<br />\n呢幾個月黎, 每次黑狗衝, 手足就退, 逃跑<br />\n但係我地宜家發現, 咁樣係唔work 既<br />\n諗住不流血, 不被捕 = 逃跑 = 流血, 被捕<br />\n背向敵人逃跑, 只會令一部份既手足被捕<br />\n係策略上, 我地be water 就係時候要適應, 將逃跑策略改為迎擊策略.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以, be water, 我地要進化<br />\n我地要be formless<br />\n敵進, 我退, 我地要流動, 但我地可以係另一處重整<br />\n速龍衝前, 我地可以守陣地, 我地可以保持隊型<br />\n我地可以防守姿態迎擊, 以遠近攻擊退敵<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Be Water and Crash</span><br />\n<br />\n當人眾敵寡, 我地仲可以crash, 可以衝擊<br />\n我地可以設一個目標<br />\n然後衝擊<br />\n我地可以使用合適工具, 達到目的<br />\n然後流動, 重組<br />\n<br />\n我地可以利用人數上優勢&mdash;側擊, 夾擊<br />\n我地可以突襲, 可以虛張聲勢<br />\n可以擾敵, 可以設陷阱<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Empty your mind, be formless, shapeless, like water&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n我地要empty our mind, 將對速龍, 防暴既恐懼, 拎走<br />\n我地要放低一些枷鎖, 進行適當自衛<br />\n我地同狗對峙時, 可以同身邊手足分享<br />\nBe Water 的真締<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"30cf79eaa27139f1b283d0b516b810598f890d21","tid":1607047,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:15:47.000Z","msg":"國慶咁大件事 緊係要約埋建制議員賀佢老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1605409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1605409</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dGVTmzV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdGVTmzV.jpg&h=c9cd4e99&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98f9c0ef34e43feca026329f79417db71606929e","tid":1607047,"uid":298707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:17:18.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"fc95fefdb737bc731c52fa0eb335673536ffc5b1","tid":1607047,"uid":298707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:20:10.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"04b5a72e76b80ac9eb6307b23a97d864565dd8fd","tid":1607047,"uid":298707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:20:32.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"5aeceef8ed73fc127b0441d500bf1fa547ae153c","tid":1607047,"uid":298707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:23:13.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"7312a2d9fbfc3c00bf593ee19ef90c5ef3144086","tid":1607047,"uid":298707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:23:28.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"5220d7cf534e9ba30b1e4518eafacc8efaec14c7","tid":1607047,"uid":298707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:23:38.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"133fb307ad1cec609c38de2f568f17064efa679f","tid":1607047,"uid":298707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:24:17.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"e0dd5c17122ff350eedf34e0664baa331571cea6","tid":1607047,"uid":298707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:24:39.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"eedf87952a2044c68368c579520e8bfdb6fae0a3","tid":1607047,"uid":298707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:24:50.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"da4d0cfbe8196fc34843387946ee4abfc6bdff3e","tid":1607047,"uid":298707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:25:02.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"02b141fc440c766ff16e94163169bb2db